name: signal-recognition-particle GTPase
classes: Acting on GTP to facilitate cellular and subcellular movement
comment: Activity is associated with the signal-recognition particle (a protein- and RNA-containing structure involved in endoplasmic-reticulum-associated protein synthesis).
